metadata.name: Rugbull #1
metadata.description: Rugbulls are the reincarnation of the original Rugblulls: Genesis collection, launched in July 2021 (https://opensea.io/collection/rugbullsgenesis). Rugby + Bull = Rugbull, got it? Anyway the bull in the shape of a rugby ball, comon, what the fuck? I say hello to all tripping guys. Just read the description of the genesis collection, that's just the ramblings of a stoned me. Also it's very similar with rug pulls, which we got tired of but we don't have a plans to rug pull you. I don't know what's going on in the market, but if it becomes successful, I will be shocked. I'm still in the NFT space, and that was my first attempts at a generative collection. By the way, the NFTs can be duplicated lol: I stupidly took the original 2021-art and re-generated them. Don't expect anything from it, but if you manage to make money on it, man, you're just the best. So okay: if it works for someone, we'll create a community, a Twitter, all that shit. And we'll develop that shit further. A collection with a background, motherfucker. When the hype starts, check the description on OpenSea, that's where I'll add the Twitter.
